extras/4ecc688cf0ffca5c0b6959f7687b9ff8.avif?t=1769186944\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>捍卫古老的传统，证明色雷斯诸神与希腊诸神一样强大，为你的王国与军队带来庇佑。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/052ac928f0e1c95db23a88df4b42ced3.poster.avif?t=1769186944\" width=616 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/052ac928f0e1c95db23a88df4b42ced3.webm?t=1769186944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/052ac928f0e1c95db23a88df4b42ced3.mp4?t=1769186944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/7e3db5d59f220140b5dabd4b7b8df654.avif?t=1769186944\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>召唤无尽的军团，或是从埃及、埃塞俄比亚、迦南和苏萨等阳光普照之地上召唤增援。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/51e0b736d6cc0f6fa04601bff8b0f415.poster.avif?t=1769186944\" width=616 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/51e0b736d6cc0f6fa04601bff8b0f415.webm?t=1769186944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/51e0b736d6cc0f6fa04601bff8b0f415.mp4?t=1769186944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553060/extras/70c845e6d49226e274fa72ea7d1b6cd5.avif?t=1769186944\" width=616 height=83 /></span><br>为门农的军队指派异邦战略家，以获得疲劳敌人或使箭塔失效等独特战略效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=